data.description: This is the house you have been waiting for!  It is in the desirable Rush Brook addition!  EDMOND SCHOOLS!  This 3 bed 2 bath house is immaculate!  It is a split plan, which gives you the privacy you crave.  The spa-like primary bath is to die for!  Separate sink vanities, a walk-in shower, soaking tub, and massive closet that leads to the laundry room are just the beginning of the amenities this home offers.  The fireplace is the design feature of the living space.  It reaches all the way to the ceiling and has a built-in cabinet and shelves beside it.  The ceiling beam and large windows finish off the space.  The open concept kitchen is gorgeous.  Top of the line stainless steel appliances, beautiful backsplash, and pops of color tie it perfectly to the rest of the house! There is a large pantry as well.  The 2 secondary bedrooms offer nice size closets.  The hall off the secondary bedrooms offers floor to ceiling storage and a built in desk nook.  The backyard is large and does not have any neighbors behind it!  The neighborhood has ponds, pool and pool house, splash pad, and playground!
